  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together water, feta cheese, yogurt, olive oil, lemon juice, garlic, oregano, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add the lamb to the marinade and mix well to coat.",
    "Thread the lamb onto the wooden skewers, leaving a small space between each piece.",
    "Grill the kebabs for 8-10 minutes per side, or until cooked through.",
    "Transfer the kebabs to a plate and garnish with parsley, if desired.",
    "Serve immediately, garnished with lemon wedges and pita bread."
